&lt;h1 id="arm-yourself-with-specific-knowledge"&gt;Arm Yourself With Specific Knowledge&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mar 25 2019&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Specific knowledge can be found by pursuing your genuine curiosity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Do you want to talk a little bit about the skills that you need, in particular specific knowledge, accountability, leverage and judgment. So, the first tweet in this area is &amp;ldquo;Arm yourself with specific knowledge accountability and leverage.&amp;rdquo; And I&amp;rsquo;ll throw in judgment as well. I don&amp;rsquo;t think you covered that in that particular tweet.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>What You'll Wish You'd Known</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/hs/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jan 2005 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/hs/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/hs/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
